HTTPov interface: Status interface for HTTPov

This is an interface for viewing the internal states of the HTTPov server;
available and running jobs and batches, and the number of clients 
currently running.

Requirements:
=============
Smarty, tested with version 2.6.26:
http://www.smarty.net/

jQuery, tested with version 1.5.1:
http://jquery.com/

TableSorter, tested with version 2.0.5b:
http://tablesorter.com
